Din!

00:55:01.740 --> 00:55:03.460
Please stop here.

00:55:03.460 --> 00:55:04.500
Come on, Nam.

00:55:05.700 --> 00:55:07.740
Hurry up.

00:55:08.260 --> 00:55:10.420
Nam! Fai!

00:55:12.160 --> 00:55:13.730
Why didn’t you tell me you’d come?

00:55:15.660 --> 00:55:18.260
And why didn’t you tell me before you’d decide to get married?

00:55:20.000 --> 00:55:22.100
Rose! Are you her?

00:55:23.580 --> 00:55:24.620
Fai!

00:55:26.800 --> 00:55:28.130
Yes, I’m Rose.

00:55:28.800 --> 00:55:31.700
Rose, if you want to get married, just marry me instead.

00:55:32.700 --> 00:55:33.500
What?

00:55:33.560 --> 00:55:37.530
Nam already told me everything. I’m not going to let my sister risking her life like that.

00:55:39.200 --> 00:55:42.820
Fai, you should talk to me. Leave Rose out of this.

00:55:42.900 --> 00:55:45.660
I don’t have anything to talk to you. I want to talk to her.

00:55:45.660 --> 00:55:49.860
Come and marry me instead. We can do it right away. How about tomorrow? Nam…

00:55:50.560 --> 00:55:51.140
Geez!

00:55:51.140 --> 00:55:51.820
You’re here?

00:55:52.180 --> 00:55:53.700
- Lom!
- I miss you so much.

00:55:53.730 --> 00:55:55.180
[Lom]: Aww, let me see your face.

00:55:55.180 --> 00:55:55.900
- Geez!
- My little boss.

00:55:55.930 --> 00:55:59.180
Fai might seem unfriendly. But deep down she’s a nice person.

00:55:59.180 --> 00:56:00.300
Please don’t worry.

00:56:00.330 --> 00:56:02.300
[Lom]: I don’t have any girls to hug lately. Come give me a hug.

00:56:02.460 --> 00:56:03.460
[Fai]: Go and hug Nam then.

00:56:03.500 --> 00:56:04.600
[Fai]: Nam!
- No.

00:56:05.060 --> 00:56:06.200
So, what’s your answer, Rose?

00:56:06.660 --> 00:56:07.460
[Lom]: Shut up.

00:56:22.930 --> 00:56:26.060
[Din]: All right then, let me officially introduce you guys to each other again.

00:56:26.330 --> 00:56:27.560
Someone seems to have lost her mind earlier.

00:56:28.960 --> 00:56:30.200
And her manners too.

00:56:30.700 --> 00:56:33.540
Hey, what the heck?

00:56:35.060 --> 00:56:38.700
This is Nam and Fai, my younger cousins.

00:56:39.900 --> 00:56:41.220
Hello, Nam.

00:56:43.740 --> 00:56:45.500
H…Hello, Fai.

00:56:46.860 --> 00:56:48.140
This is Rose.

00:56:50.360 --> 00:56:51.260
Hello.

00:56:55.360 --> 00:56:56.380
Hi.

00:57:04.330 --> 00:57:06.180
Hi…there.

00:57:10.960 --> 00:57:13.330
We’ll help arrange the wedding for you.

00:57:14.400 --> 00:57:15.700
Thank you so much.

00:57:15.700 --> 00:57:19.100
Lom told me that you’re a pro in wedding arrangement.

00:57:19.300 --> 00:57:20.900
Oh, not at all.

00:57:21.580 --> 00:57:23.420
She’s exaggerating.

00:57:24.500 --> 00:57:29.180
So, do you want to have the wedding here or at Chomchan farm?

00:57:30.360 --> 00:57:31.560
What do you say?

00:57:33.300 --> 00:57:37.100
I think it’d be safer to do it here.

00:57:37.930 --> 00:57:40.400
And how many guests would you like to invite?

00:57:42.760 --> 00:57:45.860
I want to keep it small and private.

00:57:45.860 --> 00:57:50.060
Maybe with a small corner for the VIP guests like those senior officials from the province.

00:57:50.060 --> 00:57:54.060
In case if Mr. Wasupol and his men show up, they mightn’t dare to stir up any trouble.

00:57:55.130 --> 00:57:56.580
That’s a good idea.

00:57:57.220 --> 00:58:00.260
Those senior officials can also be the witnesses for our wedding.

00:58:02.100 --> 00:58:04.420
As for your safety, let me take care of that.

00:58:04.600 --> 00:58:08.700
And about photography for a prewedding, Fai will help take care of it.

00:58:09.860 --> 00:58:11.220
Who said I’d do it?

00:58:14.000 --> 00:58:16.860
Fine. But that’s because Nam’s asked me to.

00:58:21.530 --> 00:58:27.060
Okay then, I’m going to take a look around a bit.

00:58:27.060 --> 00:58:29.220
I’ll see what I can do with the place.

00:58:29.220 --> 00:58:30.980
Then, I’ll tell the organizer to work on it.

00:58:31.500 --> 00:58:32.360
Go ahead then.

00:58:35.000 --> 00:58:38.900
Fai, come and help me take some pictures. I have to send them to my staff.

00:58:40.300 --> 00:58:41.100
Okay.

00:58:44.330 --> 00:58:47.620
Please feel free to use as many flowers as you want from my farm.

00:58:47.900 --> 00:58:49.760
I’ll tell my workers to bring them here for you.

00:58:51.900 --> 00:58:52.740
Thank you.

00:58:55.700 --> 00:58:58.700
Hey, can you stop making a sullen face?

00:59:00.600 --> 00:59:04.940
What? I haven’t said anything yet. You’re all imagining it.

00:59:06.900 --> 00:59:11.560
Fai, no matter what, I’m going to marry Rose. Please try to understand me a bit.

00:59:14.600 --> 00:59:17.900
I know, I know. Can’t you see I’m trying to cooperate?

00:59:17.900 --> 00:59:18.930
Where are you going?

00:59:19.860 --> 00:59:20.800
To get my camera.

00:59:24.530 --> 00:59:28.780
Din, did I do anything to upset Fai?

00:59:29.900 --> 00:59:32.130
She’s always like that to strangers.

00:59:32.330 --> 00:59:35.700
But once you get to know her more, she’s actually quite friendly.

00:59:43.800 --> 00:59:47.460
Sis, let’s do the prewedding photoshoot tomorrow.

00:59:48.100 --> 00:59:50.100
But it might look a little dry in the background.

00:59:56.330 --> 01:00:00.780
Then, should we do it at your farm instead? It’ll probably look prettier.

01:00:02.400 --> 01:00:05.800
Yeah, that’d be better. Can we use your farm, Rose?

01:00:07.600 --> 01:00:08.400
Sure.

